<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="ida8f7f8b9-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5" identifier="/us/usc/t10/s1584"><num value="1584">§ 1584.</num><heading> Employment of non-citizens</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Laws prohibiting the employment of, or payment of pay or expenses to, a person who is not a citizen of the United States do not apply to personnel of the Department of Defense.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="ida8f7f8ba-3a6f-11f1-a58a-d8db54b14ab5">(<ref href="/us/act/1956-08-10/ch1041">Aug. 10, 1956, ch. 1041</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/70A/118">70A Stat. 118</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/97/295/s1/20/A">Pub. L. 97–295, § 1(20)(A)</ref>, <date date="1982-10-12">Oct. 12, 1982</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/96/1290">96 Stat. 1290</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/101/510/dA/tXIV">Pub. L. 101–510, div. A, title XIV</ref>, §§ 1481(d)(1), (2), 1482(b), <date date="1990-11-05">Nov. 5, 1990</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/104/1706">104 Stat. 1706</ref>, 1709; <ref href="/us/pl/104/106/dA/tX/s1062/b">Pub. L. 104–106, div. A, title X, § 1062(b)</ref>, <date date="1996-02-10">Feb. 10, 1996</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/110/444">110 Stat. 444</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
